    "intro": "The movements below trace the chapter's argument from Sheba's tribal revolt through Joab's unchecked violence to the wise woman's surprising resolution, locating each pericope in its canonical and redemptive-historical context. Where Hebrew lexical nuance sharpens meaning, a note follows the exposition.",
